Description:
Statista Bookkeeping Pvt. Ltd. is a India based outsourcing firm that specializes in providing timely, accurate, confidential services for Big and small -sized businesses .
The office is centrally located in Srinagar (J&K) near the downtown core. STBK. tailors its services to match each client’s unique set of needs and schedules.

STBK is committed to forging business alliances with our clients as partners so they can focus on the development and expansion while we supply them with the accurate and right need to make timely and accurate business decisions for the effective business operations.

STBB has been operating in Srinagar and Delhi since 2019 as an independent Business Process Outsourcing and working with several accounting firms in the USA,UK. AUstralia and Canada. In the end of 2020, the decision was made to change the name with the sole proprietorship to Statista Bookkeeping Pvt. Ltd. and shift the business focus to concentrate our services in the areas of:
Full service BPO service for small to medium sized and Large sector proprietorship, partnerships, and corporations in the USA and Canada;
working closely with client’s accounting firm for the benefit of clients;
and training/set-up assistance.

STATISTA offers:
New Organisation with best team which is experienced in all levels of Merchant Cash Advance, US Agro Outsourcing and BANT services;
unique experience with a variety of business types including: sales, professional services, consulting, retail, large construction projects, and job costing;
customized financial reporting to provide each client and their accountant with the information they need to work on the challenging and strategic business decisions required to operate and grow.

STBK is proud of the work that we have accomplished while supporting our clients, and continually strive to maintain our commitment to delivering high quality, professional services.

En Sum Talk imaginamos y creamos la futura gestión de cliente. Ayudamos a las marcas a crear relaciones duraderas con sus clientes optimizando su experiencia. Innovamos imaginando el mañana y nos adaptamos pensando en las necesidades concretas de cada empresa o proyecto, porque sabemos que cada cliente y cada momento son diferentes. 

Aplicamos la experiencia y las últimas tecnologías para aportar valor a las empresas en cada interacción guiándoles hacia la futura gestión de clientes.

La experiencia de cliente memorable es nuestro objetivo, tanto en los servicios de atención como de venta.

