Trinity is the largest provider of readymade companies in Poland and the CEE and part of the Trinity Corporate Services Group. We are recommended by major law, audit and tax advisory firms in Poland who purchase our shelf companies on a regular basis. With offices in Poland (Warsaw, Krakow, Wroclaw, Poznan), Czech Republic (Prague), Slovakia (Bratislava), Romania (Bucharest) and Bulgaria (Sofia) we can provide shelf companies throughout the CEE region. 

Setting up a company in Poland is a time consuming, complex, frustrating and expensive process. Our Polish shelf companies are fully registered entities with flexible articles of association, an operational bank account and up-to-date accounting and tax records, all in accordance with the applicable laws. They have no history and we provide unlimited guarantees over the quality of our shelf companies. Transfer of a readymade company is a matter of hours and the investor may trade immediately. Post transfer individualization of the readymade company is also available. Our shelf company clients range from private equity firms, real estate funds, multinational enterprises, high net worth individuals to promising start ups.  We communicate fluently in English and the languages of the local offices, have dedicated German, Spanish and Italian desks, as well as Private Equity and Real Estate desks. 

We are Poland’s shelf company market leader and provide clients with a broad scope of corporate services:

•	Incorporation and registration of new companies;
•	Sale of shelf companies (and partnerships);
•	Administrative & management support for operating companies including accounting and tax compliance, payroll, domiciliary (virtual office) services, assistance with setting up of bank accounts or registrations with various authorities, company  secretarial support;
•	Liquidations or buy-back of companies.

